#. <section class="sutta" id="sn45.20"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn45.20:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.20:0.2"
msgid "2. Vihāravagga"
msgstr "2. Meditation"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.20:0.3"
msgid "20. Tatiyakukkuṭārāmasutta"
msgstr "20. At the Chicken Monastery (3rd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.17"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.20:1.1"
msgid "Pāṭaliputtanidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Pāṭaliputta."

msgctxt "sn45.20:1.2"
msgid "“‘Brahmacariyaṃ, brahmacariyan’ti, āvuso ānanda, vuccati."
msgstr "“Reverend, they speak of this thing called the ‘spiritual path’."

msgctxt "sn45.20:1.3"
msgid ""
"Katamaṃ nu kho, āvuso, brahmacariyaṃ, katamo brahmacārī, katamaṃ "
"brahmacariyapariyosānan”ti?"
msgstr ""
"What is the spiritual path? Who is someone on the spiritual path? And what "
"is the culmination of the spiritual path?”"

msgctxt "sn45.20:1.4"
msgid "“Sādhu sādhu, āvuso bhadda."
msgstr "“Good, good, Reverend Bhadda!"

msgctxt "sn45.20:1.5"
msgid ""
"Bhaddako kho te, āvuso bhadda, ummaṅgo, bhaddakaṃ paṭibhānaṃ, kalyāṇī "
"paripucchā."
msgstr ""
"Your approach and articulation are excellent, and it’s a good question. …"

msgctxt "sn45.20:1.6"
msgid "Evañhi tvaṃ, āvuso bhadda, pucchasi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn45.20:1.7"
msgid "‘brahmacariyaṃ, brahmacariyanti, āvuso ānanda, vuccati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn45.20:1.8"
msgid ""
"Katamaṃ nu kho, āvuso, brahmacariyaṃ, katamo brahmacārī, katamaṃ "
"brahmacariyapariyosānan’”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn45.20:1.9"
msgid "“Evamāvuso”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn45.20:1.10"
msgid "“Ayameva kho, āvuso, ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo brahmacariyaṃ, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "The spiritual path is simply this noble eightfold path, that is:"

msgctxt "sn45.20:1.11"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhi."
msgstr ""
"right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, "
"right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion."

msgctxt "sn45.20:1.12"
msgid "Yo kho, āvuso, iminā ariyena aṭṭhaṅgikena maggena samannāgato—"
msgstr "Someone who possesses this noble eightfold path"

msgctxt "sn45.20:1.13"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati brahmacārī."
msgstr "is called someone on the spiritual path."

msgctxt "sn45.20:1.14"
msgid "Yo kho, āvuso, rāgakkhayo dosakkhayo mohakkhayo—"
msgstr "The ending of greed, hate, and delusion."

msgctxt "sn45.20:1.15"
msgid "idaṃ brahmacariyapariyosānan”ti."
msgstr "This is the culmination of the spiritual path.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.20:1.16"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.20:1.17"
msgid "Tīṇi suttantāni ekanidānāni."
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.20:1.18"
msgid "Vihāravaggo dutiyo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.20:2.1"
msgid "Dve vihārā ca sekkho ca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.20:2.2"
msgid "uppādā apare duve;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.20:2.3"
msgid "Parisuddhena dve vuttā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.20:2.4"
msgid "kukkuṭārāmena tayoti."
msgstr ""
